Name: The Call that Comes from a Lost Land
AttributesDescription:
Each time the Resonators in the team cast Resonance Liberation, Resonance Skill DMG of all Resonators in the team is increased by 62.5%, stacking up to 2 times for 30s.

This Token can be used up to 2 times in Whimpering Wastes.
BgDescription: The traveler clung to the belief that the blood flowing through his veins was tied to a lineage from a land long forgotten by Rinascita. The visions of cold and fjords relentlessly plagued his mind. Finally, he poured all his savings into a ship, set sail, and never returned.
